Locate your 7 Days To Die install folder (default: C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Steam\\steamapps\\common)
Open the 7DaysToDie → Data → Worlds folder
Download the map (it comes as a .rar archive)
Extract the archive (e.g. with WinRAR https://www.win-rar.com/download.html?&L=0)
Place the extracted map folder (single folder) into the Worlds directory
Start or restart the game – enjoy!
